ons about optimization are introduced, including optimization algorithms for hypergraph matching, support vector machine and bilevel optimization approach for hyperparameter selection in machine learning. With these optimization tools, one can deal with data more efficiently.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aMATHEMATICS / Probability & Statistics / Regression Analysis.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2z978311117804208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishz978311131920908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023z9783111318608oZDB-23-DMA40uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-3175-340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759831753423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759831753/original  a978-3-11-117804-2  DG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2b2023  a978-3-11-131920-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MTPY  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DMAb2023